My Vim configurations files.

I used Pathogen to organize the plugins.

The following languages are "supported":

C, Python, PHP

If you want to make a suggestion, you are welcome.

Bye

---

What to do:

    git clone --recursive https://github.com/mateusbraga/vim_mab

    cd
    ln -s (vim_mab)/.vim .vim
    ln -s (vim_mab)/.vimrc .vimrc

    # Make command-t
    cd vim_mab/.vim/bundle/command-t
    rake make

